author: Animalogic
description:
Pigs are smart, social, and way more sensitive than we think. If you want to help them but don’t know where to start, FarmKind makes it simple. They research the charities creating real change and send your full donation straight to the work. Use code 'animalogic' for a 50 percent boost on your donation: https://www.farmkind.giving/animalogic

Did you know that pigs are as smart as a three-year-old child? They can solve puzzles, recognize themselves in mirrors, and even learn video games.
